column1: Daily Weather Observations for Moruya, New South Wales for January 2021
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Saturday  9 October 2021   IDCJDW2085.202101
Most observations from Moruya Heads Pilot Station, but some from Moruya Airport.
Temperature, humidity, pressure, cloud and rainfall observations are from Moruya Heads Pilot Station {station 069018}
Wind observations are from Moruya Airport AWS {station 069148}
